uot;_blank&quot; data-stringify-link=&quot;https://gradle.org/&quot; data-sk=&quot;tooltip_parent&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;Gradle&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We have noticed a rise in recruiting impersonations across the industry, where scammers attempt to access candidates&#39; personal and financial information through fake interviews and offers. All Fingerprint recruiting email communications will always come from the @fingerprint.com domain. Any outreach claiming to be from Fingerprint via other sources should be ignored.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h4&gt;About the Role&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an&amp;nbsp; Enterprise Sales Director to lead high-value, multi-million-dollar deals with Fortune 500 and global enterprises. This role is ideal for a consultative sales leader with a deep understanding of complex enterprise sales, strategic account planning, and MEDDICC methodology. You will be responsible for developing and executing long-term account strategies that drive revenue growth and deepen customer relationships.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable managing&amp;nbsp; a strategic book of business, focusing on high-value enterprise accounts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skilled in implementing account planning strategies and running regular deal reviews to drive engagement across large enterprise accounts,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiar with supporting the teamâ€™s pipeline generation efforts including running regular team PG days, managing outbound cadences, supporting marketing-driven ABM programs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Uses detailed data and reporting to continuously review the health and success of their business including pipeline metrics, opportunity aging reports, deal qualification criteria,&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understands how to manage a quarterly forecast and hold the team accountable to forecast accuracy and pipeline coverage ratios.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead complex deal negotiations involving multiple stakeholders, procurement, and legal teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use MEDDPICC to de-risk deals, improve win rates, and drive accurate forecasting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strong executive relationships, acting as a trusted advisor to enterprise clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate cross-functionally with Product, Customer Success, and Marketing to drive adoption and retention.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Present business cases and ROI models to justify investment in our solutions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop deep industry expertise to anticipate market trends and customer needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive thought leadership by participating in key industry events and conferences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Qualifications&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;7-10+ years of enterprise sales experience, with a strong focus on strategic selling, including value selling methodologies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated success in closing multi-million-dollar, multi-year SaaS contracts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Expert in or MEDDPICC, with a proven ability to manage risk in complex deals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong executive presence and ability to engage C-level decision-makers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing global accounts and large buying groups.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional strategic thinking, problem-solving, and negotiation skills.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable working with cross-functional teams to drive enterprise adoption.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background in AI, cybersecurity, identity, analytics, or infrastructure SaaS is highly preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;487&quot; data-end=&quot;970&quot;&gt;&lt;em data-stringify-type=&quot;italic&quot;&gt;The base salary range for this role is $175,000 - $210,000 + Variable. For cash compensation, we set standard ranges for all US based roles based on function, level and geographic location, benchmarked against similar stage growth companies. In order to be compliant with local legislation, as well as to provide greater transparency to candidates, we share salary ranges on all job postings regardless of desired hiring location. Final offer amounts are determined by multiple factors including geographic location as well as candidate experience and expertise, and may vary from the amounts listed above.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;We have noticed a rise in recruiting impersonations across the industry, where scammers attempt to access candidates&#39; personal and financial information through fake interviews and offers. All Fingerprint recruiting email communications will always come from the @fingerprint.com domain. Any outreach claiming to be from Fingerprint via other sources should be ignored.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Offers vary depending on, but not limited to, relevant experience, education, certifications/licenses, skills, training, and market conditions.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Due to regulatory and security reasons, thereâ€™s a small number of countries where we cannot have Fingerprint teammates based.&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Additionally, because Fingerprint is an all-remote company and people can join our workforce from almost any country, we do not sponsor visas. Fingerprint teammates need to be authorized to work from their home location&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
